text:
Hey,
First time I met you in Summer'18 where you were high on setting up new records 
You- "Aaj m 14 hrs soya hu!" 
Me-  "Late kyu?" 
Ayush- "Tum dono ko jhargadne k waje s group s nikala ja rha h."
I still don't know the accuracy of the project, but your accuracy of cracking good jokes increased manifold times. Asking your phone number is the cringest thing I have ever done with a guy. Also, after getting the number + 2 minutes of silence I said, "ab mera bhi rakh lo" :P
You were the only person who didn't ask "Kyu" when I said I am thinking of not making the memoirs public. That's how we connect so well.
I learned to be positive and patient from you but yeh bhulne ki bimari mujhe bhi lag gyi (Should I be grateful to you? no)
In the most annoyed version of you, I admire that the max thing you do is check messages late :')[Tears of happiness].
PS- Tumhara memoir invalid h kyuki group leader m bhi thi and "haha" emoji are missing.
